title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I had to do a media exam last year and I mentioned you in my case study for American horror story as part of the user generated content creators. I’m coming back to your channel for season 8, but I can never watch your lives because we are 4 hours ahead of you here.

Sorry to have missed this, no notification again... YouTube really sucks with that lately.
Adina Porter was in seasons 1, 6, 7 & now 8 will be her fourth season.

My FAVORITES are Asylum, Coven, Freak Show, Cult.... The others are Okay... Murder House's ending had a great surprise.  Hotel is my least favorite.  The storylines were weak, way too much sex & violence overkill, and Gaga's "acting" was cringe worthy sadly for me. Was Queenie's death necessary?? 😑 So SAD!
I'm do anxious i check ur channel all the time for updates i wish people were looking into this season like they were for season 6 but thats because it was a mystery season
